Luna Luminance
==============

Introduction
------------

This is a puzzle game. The goal is to make a 3x3 block of one color.

Playing
-------

Left click to rotate rows and right click to invert column colors to
make a 3x3 block of one color.

Currently, the game does not end when the blocks hit the top of the
screen.

Controls
--------
left click   rotate a row
right click  invert a column
